---
title: Irish Sirloin Steak and Cheesy Chipotle Sauce with golden smashed potatoes
description: A deliciously decadent and spicy chipotle cheese sauce smothers 100% Irish sirloin steak accompanied with tender green beans and crispy smashed baby potatoes in this deceptively simple recipe.
